analysis: The agent omitted the required "contactMethod": "Email" parameter in its function call, resulting in a mismatch with the expected function signature and a failure to retrieve matching suppliers with contact details.

The agent failed due to argument value casing mismatches: it used "Moderate" and "Dynamic" instead of the expected lowercase "moderate" and "dynamic" for the function parameters, causing the evaluator to not recognize the function call as matching.

The agent incorrectly specified "outputDetail": "Detailed" instead of the required "outputDetail": "Summary", failing to match the expected function call parameters for TrendAnalysisTool_generateMarketInsights.

The agent added an unsupported "weatherDetail" parameter to the FlightStatus_checkFlightAndWeather function call. The function only accepts "airportCode" and "flightNumber" parameters, so the call did not match the expected format.

The agent failed to include the required "ratingThreshold": "good" parameter when calling GameFinder_analyzeUserInterestForGames, missing an explicit user constraint about game quality. This resulted in an incomplete and non-matching function call.
